I"g<p>Welcome to my website. I hope you can find useful and interesting information about my research work. I am a titular professor in the <a href="http://www.ler.uam.mx/es/UAMLerma/DSIC" target="_blank">Deparment of Information Systems and Communications</a> of the <a href="http://www.ler.uam.mx" target="_blank">Universidad Autónoma Metropolitana</a> in Lerma, Mexico.</p>

<h2 id="research-interests">Research interests:</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Routing in large-scale networks</li>
  <li>Graph theory</li>
  <li>Distributed algorithms</li>
  <li>Complex systems</li>
</ul>

